entries.femaleVariant: Dunno 'bout that. You been sittin' here since they shut this place down. Don't look like you adapted nothin'.
I used to be somebody. Used to supervise this whole project.
Yeah, well. Went out to the Badlands yesterday. Down to that dam. Caught me a goddamn fish.
Pssh, ain't no such thing these days. An' if you did catch a mutant whatever, don't eat it. You'll be squirt-shittin' the goddamn rainbow.
Nah, the fuck, choom. Gonna sell the sucker.
